---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About JCS - 15+ Years of Trusted Service | Delhi-NCR">
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box}body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;line-height:1.6;color:#1f2937;margin:0;background:#fafafa}
.hero{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e40af 0%,#7c3aed 100%);color:#fff;padding:100px 20px 80px;text-align:center}
.hero h1{font-size:2.8rem;margin:0 0 20px;font-weight:700}
.hero p{font-size:1.3rem;opacity:.95;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto}
.container{max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 20px}
.section{margin-bottom:80px}
.section h2{font-size:2rem;color:#1f2937;margin:0 0 25px;text-align:center}
.section p{font-size:1.1rem;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:20px}
.stats{background:#fff;padding:60px 40px;border-radius:12px;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08);display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:40px;text-align:center;margin:60px 0}
.stat strong{display:block;font-size:3rem;color:#3b82f6;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px}
.stat span{color:#6b7280;font-size:1rem}
.values{background:#f9fafb;padding:60px 40px;border-radius:12px;margin:60px 0}
.values h3{color:#1f2937;font-size:1.5rem;margin:0 0 30px}
.values ul{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));gap:25px}
.values li{background:#fff;padding:25px;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid #3b82f6}
.values li strong{display:block;color:#1f2937;margin-bottom:8px;font-size:1.1rem}
.values li p{margin:0;color:#6b7280;font-size:.95rem}
.cta{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e40af 0%,#7c3aed 100%);color:#fff;padding:80px 40px;text-align:center;border-radius:12px;margin:60px 0}
.cta h2{font-size:2.2rem;margin:0 0 15px}
.cta p{font-size:1.2rem;opacity:.95;margin:0 0 35px}
.cta .btn{display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#1e40af;padding:18px 40px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:1.1rem;transition:all .3s}
.cta .btn:hover{transform:scale(1.05);box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(255,255,255,.3)}
@media(max-width:768px){.hero h1{font-size:2rem}.stats{grid-template-columns:1fr}.values ul{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>

<div class="hero">
  <h1>15+ Years of Trusted Service</h1>
  <p>From a small practice to Delhi-NCR's reliable partner for MSME compliance—our story is built on client success</p>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>
      Jaraut Consultancy Services (JCS) began in 2010 with a simple mission: help small businesses stay compliant without the complexity and cost of hiring full-time specialists. What started as a two-person team handling GST returns has grown into a full-service consultancy supporting over 100 MSMEs across Delhi-NCR.
    </p>
    <p>
      We're not a faceless corporation. We're a group of professionals—accountants, HR specialists, legal advisors, and hospitality coordinators—who've worked in the trenches. We understand the 11 PM panic when you realize a GST deadline is tomorrow. We've seen businesses get hit with ₹50,000+ penalties for missing PF filings. That's why we exist: to take that stress off your plate.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our clients range from manufacturing units in Mayapuri to coaching institutes in Janakpuri, from tech startups to traditional family businesses. What they all have in common: they want to focus on growth, not paperwork.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="stats">
    <div class="stat">
      <strong>15+</strong>
      <span>Years Experience</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <strong>100+</strong>
      <span>MSMEs Supported</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <strong>15+</strong>
      <span>Industries Covered</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <strong>Zero</strong>
      <span>Late Filing Penalties</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Our Vision</h2>
    <p style="text-align:center;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1f2937;font-weight:500">
      To be known as a specialist, process-driven, and most trusted outsource partner for MSMEs in Delhi-NCR—delivering compliance and support at competitive costs.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p style="text-align:center;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1f2937;font-weight:500">
      Excellence in Service. Establish JCS as the preferred provider of accounts, HR, legal, and hospitality services—delivering uninterrupted, reliable, and best-in-class support.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="values">
    <h3>Our Core Values</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Honesty</strong>
        <p>We tell you what you need to hear, not what you want to hear. If your books are a mess, we'll say so—and fix it.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Integrity</strong>
        <p>No shortcuts. No under-the-table deals. We do things the right way, every time.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Respect</strong>
        <p>Your time is valuable. We respond within 24 hours, show up on time, and deliver what we promise.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Fairness</strong>
        <p>Transparent pricing. No hidden fees. You know exactly what you're paying for.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Purposefulness</strong>
        <p>Every service we offer solves a real problem. We don't sell you things you don't need.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Can-Do Together</strong>
        <p>Your success is our success. We're partners, not vendors.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Responsibility</strong>
        <p>If we miss a deadline, we own it—and we cover the penalty. That's our guarantee.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Citizenship</strong>
        <p>We believe in building stronger businesses that contribute to stronger communities.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Caring</strong>
        <p>We genuinely care about your business. When you're stressed, we step up.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Why Choose JCS?</h2>
    <p>
      There are hundreds of CA firms and HR consultants in Delhi. Here's what makes us different:
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>We're process-driven, not person-dependent.</strong> Your work doesn't stop if someone's on leave. We have systems, backups, and documented processes.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>We specialize in MSMEs.</strong> We understand tight cash flows, seasonal businesses, and lean teams. Our pricing and services reflect that reality.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>We're available when you need us.</strong> Yes, even on WhatsApp at 9 PM when you have a question about tomorrow's GST filing.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>We've seen it all.</strong> From labor court cases to TDS mismatches to PF inspector visits—we've handled thousands of compliance situations and know how to navigate them.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="cta">
    <h2>Ready to Work Together?</h2>
    <p>Let's talk about your business and how we can support your growth</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn">Get in Touch</a>
  </div>
</div>
</Base>
